description:
Danny is working overtime to recap all the Bravo-goodness gifted upon us this week. In this bonus, he recaps Andy's insane baby shower and this week's Vanderpump Rules, which featured a Billie Lee & Lala showdown, a 70s roller party, and more.


#PumpRules Recap: 17:01ish
